data.description: Major price improvement on this CBS home w/ no HOA! Priced below it’s value— just check the comps for 4 bdrm pool homes. County zoning allows for Airbnb or short term rental capabilities making this home a great investment opportunity! This spaciously designed 4 bdrm, 2 bthrm home has 2,481 sq.ft. of living space. You'll appreciate the impact windows throughout! Enjoy the private pool & fenced backyard with thriving mango & banana trees perfect for entertaining guests & al fresco dining. An abundance of pavers in the front & back yard. Plenty of room to park your trucks, boats & toys!
